where ğ´ğ‘™âˆ’1 (ğ‘›) is the offloading decision after user ğ‘› changes state. The specific update rules are as follows:

ğ´ğ‘™âˆ’1 (ğ‘›) = [ğ‘ğ‘™1âˆ’1, ğ‘ğ‘™2âˆ’1, â€¦ , ğ‘ğ‘›ğ‘™âˆ’1 âŠ• 1, â€¦ , ğ‘ğ‘™ğ‘âˆ’1]

